e cu caracter personal, ce vom face cu ele și cât timp vor fi păstrate.','Legal document cookie policyYou have the following rights with respect to your personal data:'=>'Ai următoarele drepturi asupra datelor cu caracter personal:','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleYour rights with respect to personal data'=>'Drepturile tale asupra datelor cu caracter personal','Legal document cookie policySharing data'=>'Partajarea datelor','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titlePlaced cookies'=>'Cookie-uri plasate','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleSocial media'=>'Media socială','Legal document cookie policyBecause these cookies are marked as tracking cookies, we ask your permission to place these.'=>'Deoarece aceste cookie-uri sunt clasificate ca fiind cookie-uri de urmărire, îți cerem permisiunea pentru a le plasa.','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleAdvertising cookies'=>'Cookie-uri publicitare','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleStatistics cookies'=>'Cookie-uri statistice','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleTechnical or functional cookies'=>'Cookie-uri tehnice sau funcționale','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleCookies'=>'Cookie-uri','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleThird parties'=>'Terți','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleConsent'=>'Consimțământ','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleWhat is a web beacon?'=>'Ce este un web beacon?','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleWhat are scripts?'=>'Ce sunt scripturile?','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleWhat are cookies?'=>'Ce sunt cookie-urile?','Legal document cookie policy:paragraph titleIntroduction'=>'Introducere','EU'=>'UE','US'=>'S.U.A.','Privacy Statement'=>'Declarație de confidențialitate','If enabled, the cookie warning will not show for countries without a cookie law, and will adjust consent management depending on supported privacy laws'=>'Dacă opțiunea este activată, avertizarea cookie nu va